m using solution quotation ID, item number and parameter UUID."/><PropertyValue Property="LongDescription" String="Retrieves convergent charging date parameters for a subscription item using solution quotation ID, item number and parameter UUID. Retrieved details include charge plan used value, date value, characteristic value and BRF function ID."/></Record></PropertyValue></Record></Annotation></Annotations><Annotations Target="API_BUS_SOLUTION_QUOTATION_SRV.API_BUS_SOLUTION_QUOTATION_SRV_Entities/A_BusSolnQtanItemNmrcParam" xmlns="http://docs.oasis-open.org/odata/ns/edm"><Annotation Term="Capabilities.ReadRestrictions"><Record><PropertyValue Property="Description" String="Retrieves convergent charging numeric parameters for a subscription item."/><PropertyValue Property="LongDescription" String="Retrieves convergent charging numeric parameters for a subscription item. The details include charge plan parameter UUID, used value, numeric value, characteristic value and BRF function ID."/><PropertyValue Property="ReadByKeyRestrictions"><Record><PropertyValue Property="Description" String="Retrieves convergent charging numeric parameters for a subscription item using solution quotation ID, item number and parameter UUID."/><PropertyValue Property="LongDescription" String="Retrieves convergent charging numeric parameters in subscription item using solution quotation ID, item number and parameter UUID. Retrieved details include charge plan used value, numeric value, characteristic value and BRF function ID."/></Record></PropertyValue></Record></Annotation></Annotations><Annotations Target="API_BUS_SOLUTION_QUOTATION_SRV.API_BUS_SOLUTION_QUOTATION_SRV_Entities/A_BusSolnQtanItemStrParam" xmlns="http://docs.oasis-open.org/odata/ns/edm"><Annotation Term="Capabilities.ReadRestrictions"><Record><PropertyValue Property="Description" String="Retrieves convergent charging string parameters for a subscription item."/><PropertyValue Property="LongDescription" String="Retrieves convergent charging string parameters for a subscription item. The details include charge plan parameter UUID, used value, string value, characteristic value and BRF function ID."/><PropertyValue Property="ReadByKeyRestrictions"><Record><PropertyValue Property="Description" String="Retrieves convergent charging string parameters for a subscription item using solution quotation ID, item number and parameter UUID."/><PropertyValue Property="LongDescription" String="Retrieves convergent charging string parameters in subscription item using solution quotation ID, item number and parameter UUID. Retrieved details include charge plan used value, string value, characteristic value and BRF function ID."/></Record></PropertyValue></Record></Annotation></Annotations><Annotations Target="API_BUS_SOLUTION_QUOTATION_SRV.API_BUS_SOLUTION_QUOTATION_SRV_Entities/A_BusSolnQtanItemTblParam" xmlns="http://docs.oasis-open.org/odata/ns/edm"><Annotation Term="Capabilities.ReadRestrictions"><Record><PropertyValue Property="Description" String="Retrieves convergent charging table parameters for a subscription item."/><PropertyValue Property="LongDescription" String="Retrieves convergent charging table parameters for a subscription item. The details include charge plan parameter UUID, used value and string value of the redefined table ID."/><PropertyValue Property="ReadByKeyRestrictions"><Record><PropertyValue Property="Description" String="Retrieves convergent charging table parameters for a subscription item using solution quotation ID, item number and parameter UUID."/><PropertyValue Property="LongDescription" String="Retrieves convergent charging table parameters for a subscription item using solution quotation ID, item number and parameter UUID. Retrieved details include charge plan used value and string value of the redefined table ID."/></Record></PropertyValue></Record></Annotation></Annotations><Annotations Target="API_BUS_SOLUTION_QUOTATION_SRV.API_BUS_SOLUTION_QUOTATION_SRV_Entities