umer specifies by passing the solution quotation ID and item number."/></Record></PropertyValue></Record><Record><PropertyValue Property="NavigationProperty" NavigationPropertyPath="to_PriceElement"/><PropertyValue Property="InsertRestrictions"><Record><PropertyValue Property="Description" String="Creates price element data for a specific expense item."/><PropertyValue Property="LongDescription" String="Creates the price element data for a specific expense item, which the consumer specifies by passing the solution quotation ID and item number."/></Record></PropertyValue></Record><Record><PropertyValue Property="NavigationProperty" NavigationPropertyPath="to_BusinessSolutionQuotation"/><PropertyValue Property="ReadRestrictions"><Record><PropertyValue Property="Description" String="Retrieves the solution quotation header for a specific expense item."/><PropertyValue Property="LongDescription" String="Retrieves the details of the solution quotation header for a specific expense item. The details include transaction type, description, organization data, and so on. Consumers must pass two key fields: solution quotation ID and item number."/></Record></PropertyValue></Record><Record><PropertyValue Property="NavigationProperty" NavigationPropertyPath="to_ServiceOrder"/><PropertyValue Property="ReadRestrictions"><Record><PropertyValue Property="Description" String="Retrieves the follow-up service order item for a specific expense item."/><PropertyValue Property="LongDescription" String="Retrieves the follow-up service order item details of a specific expense item, which the consumer specifies by passing the solution quotation ID and item number. The details include service order, solution quotation, items, and their relation."/></Record></PropertyValue></Record><Record><PropertyValue Property="NavigationProperty" NavigationPropertyPath="to_Text"/><PropertyValue Property="ReadRestrictions"><Record><PropertyValue Property="Description" String="Retrieves the texts for a specif